<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB06497</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT MODERNIZING THE REGULATION OF HEALTH FACILITIES AND SERVICES, AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR, REPEALING FOR THE PURPOSE REPUBLIC ACT NO. 4226, OTHERWISE KNOWN AS THE "HOSPITAL LICENSURE ACT"</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Modernizing The Regulation Of Health Facilities And Services</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Renames the Health Bureau of Health Facilities and Services (HFSRB) to the Bureau of Health Facilities and Services (BHFS) which shall be authorized to establish and prescribe rules, regulations, and standards in the construction and operation of health facilities; inspect and monitor for continued compliance; implement a classification system; approve building plans and construction design; collect fees; grant regulatory authorizations such as permits and licenses; and conduct administrative hearing and impose penalties. </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : ‚ÄúHealth Facilities and Services Regulation Act.‚Äù</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>TAN, ANGELINA &quot;HELEN&quot; D.L. M.D., YAP, VICTOR A., VILLARICA, HENRY R., ROMAN, GERALDINE B., ROMERO, MICHAEL ODYLON L., SUANSING, ESTRELLITA B., ROBES, FLORIDA &quot;RIDA&quot; P., SY-ALVARADO, &quot;KUYA&quot; JOSE ANTONIO R., ERIGUEL, SANDRA Y., M.D., LOYOLA, DAHLIA A., VERGARA, ROSANNA &quot;RIA&quot;, UNGAB, ISIDRO T., GARCIA, JOSE ENRIQUE &quot;JOET&quot; III S., MOMO, ROMEO S., BASCUG, ALFEL M., BORDADO, GABRIEL JR. H., GAITE, FERDINAND R., GO, MARK O., NATIVIDAD-NAGA&Ntilde;O, MARICEL G., MD., ROMULO, ROMAN T., TUTOR, KRISTINE ALEXIE B., ROMUALDEZ, FERDINAND MARTIN G., SANGCOPAN, AMIHILDA J., ARENAS, ROSE MARIE &quot;BABY&quot; J.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2020-03-05</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></t